team/apps/2307170/extras/3e1901deba85747870971c4d27b1a81a.avif?t=1771357685\" width=780 height=100 /></span>Every run is randomly generated, with its own set of challenges and twists that will keep you on your toes. Every upgrade tweaks the experience, creating various synergies. So even if you struggle to keep up with the pressure, there’s always a way to turn the tides of the battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/f810c7188f796a6997fe29b5dcc753f7.poster.avif?t=1771357685\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/f810c7188f796a6997fe29b5dcc753f7.webm?t=1771357685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/f810c7188f796a6997fe29b5dcc753f7.mp4?t=1771357685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
